quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  68,16,"Aray nde min maandina mo e hoore kinal."
  68,17,"Min njarribor …ďe wano Min njarribornoo jey…ďe ngesa mba : fewndo …ďeen ngoo…óndunoo pellet, …ďe co√Īat ba subaka ko …ďe daw…ďe."
  68,18,"…ďe itti tinaani [wi'ide] :"Si Allah ja…ďii"."
  68,19,"Jayngol immori ka Joomi maa ari huu…ďiti ba tawi he…ďe …óaanii."
  68,20,"Ba wa'iti wa jemma …ďaleejo."
  68,21,"∆Āe noddindiri bimmbi oon :"
  68,22,""Kori ndawee ta ngesa mon, si tawii ko on so√Īoo…ďe"."
  68,23,"∆Āe pokkiti he…ďe …óuumbo."
  68,24,"Won'de "miskiino woo naatataa e mabba hannde"."
  68,25,"∆Āe ndawidi e …óawugol [wa'asu…ďe …ďeen] ko …ďe e…ď…ďu…ďe."
  68,26,"Nde …ďe nji'unoo ba, …ďe mbi'i: "Pellet, min majjii [laawol ngol]"."
  68,27,"wurin ko min …óawaa…ďe!"."
  68,28,"∆Āur…óo …ďe mo∆ī∆īude oon wi'i: "mi wi'anaano on : haanii ko cubbunhino…óon?""
  68,29,"∆Āe mb'i: "Senaare woodanii Joomi amen ! Pellet, hari ko min too√Ī…ďe"."
  68,30,"Wo…ó…ďe e ma…ď…ďe feewtiti …ďeya, he…ďe pelindira."
  68,31,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Ee bone amen ! Pellet, hari ko min bew…ďe."
  68,32,"Hino gasa ka Joomi amen wattitana min …ďuri baan …óon mo∆ī∆īude. Ko ka Joomi amen ko min reer…óube e [ya'afeede] ."
  68,33,"Ko noon tigi woni le…ďte …óeen; ko lette La'akara …óeen non …ďuri manude, sinno he…ďe nganndunoo !"
  68,34,"Pellet, hino woodani gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďeen ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe, Aljannaaji ne'ema."
  68,35,"Kere Min mba…óay jebbilii…ďe …ďeen wano bon…ďe …ďeen?"
  68,36,"Ko he…ďi on, si …óon √Īaawira noon?"
  68,37,"Kaa ho…óon mari deftere, nde janngoton e mum?"
  68,38,"Pellet, ko woodani on e mayre, ko ko cu…ďoto…óon."
  68,39,"Ka ko podooje woodani on e amen, koolnii…óe haa √Ďande Darngal, won'de pellet, hino woodani on ko √Īaawoton kon?"
  68,40,"La…ďndii …ďe ko hommbo e ma…ď…ďe fawtanii…ďe …óuum?"
  68,41,"Kaa ko kafidii…ďe woodani …ďe? yoo …ďe ngaddu kafidii…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, si tawii ko …ďe gooŇču…ďe !"
  68,42,"√Ďande belenru √Īoroytee, …ďe noddee e cujjugol kono …ďe mbaawataa."